@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Space Alert Guide";
}

<style>
.icon {
    width: 20px;
}

.buttonicon {
    width: 25px;
    vertical-align: bottom;
}
</style>

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Reminders</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><img src="~/lib/Images/SpaceAlert/b.png" class="buttonicon" /> actions are <i>not</i> limited to 1<span class="cross"></span> per station per turn</li>
                <li>Lower white <img src="~/lib/Images/SpaceAlert/b.png" class="buttonicon" /> <span class="arrow"></span> a full reactor still depletes a fuel rod</li>
                <li>Rockets target the closest threat (on any trajectory)
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tie: lowest numbered token</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Delay: the <i>next</i> action slot will become empty</li>
                <li>Delays are not cumulative, max 1 per turn</li>
                <li>Battlebots can never be transferred to another player</li>
                <li>Limit 1 battlebot squad per player</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<h3>Threats</h3>
<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>In order (1-8, &alpha;-&epsilon;) each threat moves then performs actions</li>
                <li>After performing Z action, the threat ...
                    <ul>
                        <li>no longer affected by players' actions</li>
                        <li>takes no more actions and players have survived it</li>
                        <li>if intruder: remove its oval (except: Slimes, Contamination)</li>
                        <li>if malfunction: effected system is unrepairable</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Teleportation ignores obstructions or reactions to movement
                    <ul>
                        <li>teleporter's action</li>
                        <li>space-time vortex</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Special movements ignore effects if <i>passing through</i> a station
                    <ul>
                        <li>Heroic movement</li>
                        <li>Squad Leader's action</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Internal threats taking bonus damage: +1 <i>total</i> extra damage
                    <ul>
                        <li>Battlebot Uprising</li>
                        <li>Power Pack Overload</li>
                        <li>Power System Overload</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Multiple malfunctions at same station:
                    <ul>
                        <li>repair actions ignore unrepairable malfunctions</li>
                        <li>prioritize lowest number token, regardless of trajectory position</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<h3>Damage</h3>
<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Refers to physically adding a red block</li>
                <li>Rockets target closest threat, break ties in favor of lowest number</li>
                <li>Damage from internal threats is <i>not</i> reduced by shields; exceptions:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Ninja rocket attack</li>
                        <li>Pulse Cannon Short Circuit backfire effect</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ol>
                <li>Determine which threats are targeted by which weapons</li>
                <li>For each threat: 
                    <ol>
                        <li>Add the strength of all targeting weapons</li>
                        <li>Reduce strength by shield points</li>
                        <li>Damage = Strength - Shield</li>
                    </ol>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<h3>Interceptors</h3>
<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Interceptors attack on takeoff turn</li>
                <li>Only one player can be in space</li>
                <li>Knockouts or delays from threats do not affect pilot</li>
                <li>Delay from failed computer maintenance does not affect pilot</li>
                <li>Ultrafast return knocks out the pilot, disables bots</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
